text: Copper Sky is a 1957 American western movie directed by Charles Marquis Warren and starring Jeff Morrow, Coleen Gray, Strother Martin, Paul Brinegar, John Pickard. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1957 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Charles Marquis Warren
